[[File:Filfest2010image.jpg|thumb|200px]]

The '''Oaxaca International Literature Competition''' also known as '''El Concurso Internacional De Literatura Oaxaca''' is an "event within an event", where the main event is the [[Oaxaca International Independent Film and Video Festival,Oaxaca International Independent Film and Video Festival|Oaxaca International Independent Film and Video Festival]] also known as '''Festival Internacional De Cine Independiente y Video Oaxaca'''. The two events are held each November in the Mexican city of [[Oaxaca, Oaxaca|Oaxaca]]. The festival is an official cultural event of the city of [[Oaxaca de Juarez]].

The competition is intended to provide a forum for writers to display their talents to those involved in cinema.

