{{more citations needed|date=September 2016}}
'''Taha Baban''' is a [[Kurdish people|Kurdish]] writer and artist.

He was born in [[Suleymania]], Iraq and has written a number of books demonstrating the crimes of the former regime led by [[Saddam Hussein]].<ref>[http://www.worldcat.org/search?qt=worldcat_org_all&q=Taha+Baban WorldCat]</ref> Taha Baban initiated the annual Baban Golden Prize in 1970, which is awarded to actors considered to have given the best performance of the year.

